        Parameters:

        level - an integer that represents the level the user is currently on.
        gridSizeX - an integer that represents the horizontal length of the grid.
        gridSizeY - an integer that represents the vertical length of the grid.
        offSetX - an integer that represents the offset due to screen size.
        xBlocks - an integer that represents the size of the grid.
